venue.name: Kinky Boots at the Al Hirschfeld Theatre

tip.text: Scallops with mash were amazing and should not be missed, the mojitos were of interesting varieties and should be tried. Chilean seabass looked like modern art :) and was a hearty and great choice.
Get a table away from the bar and with a view, the shrimp toast is amazing and fish tacos were light and refreshing. Fish dip was a fantastic starter as well.
